We'll put it in now and 'rhett' it

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:13.860
You put the stones on top to keep it down

00:06:18.700 --> 00:06:24.420
We keep it in here for 7 to eleven days.

00:06:26.620 --> 00:06:36.040
You then take it out and break it. And if it breaks 'clean' (the outer skin come off) it is ready for taking out and spreading....

